commit.message:
Loosen vim9script detection to match new arguments

`vim9script` can have arguments, for example Vim patch 8.2.2222
introduced `noclear`. (vim/vim@2b32700dabf392566d8e9fef76e0d587a891ee3e)

Also cover the optional leading `:` in `:vim9script`.
FIX #303 Handle whitespace=no for comment types that use commentstring_rx
